section.div: A .Net Core port of Sharpii for use on other OS's

div.p: Hi! I've done work on many small projects, most recently the Konpeki Discord Bot, a Framework for creating a modern Discord bot with Node.js. I'm also the current maintainer for Sharpii-NetCore, a cross-platform tool used for homebrew file modifications.
